divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I was outside letting my dogs out when I heard a low whirring sound. I looked up and saw 4 lights, 2 of which were changing colors. I was scared and told my parents. They told me to report it to you guys so I came in here to do so. This all took place at 9:07 PM EST today, March 19, 2005. It was a little cloudy, but there were breaks in the clouds which allowed me to see this. After I saw this small detail, it flew quickly west.
